# DATATHON 2026 - The Gridbreaker: De bai vong 1 va barem diem

Nguon: `De thi Vong 1.pdf`

## 1. Tong quan de bai

Cuoc thi su dung bo du lieu mo phong hoat dong cua mot doanh nghiep thoi trang thuong mai dien tu tai Viet Nam, trong giai doan 04/07/2012 den 31/12/2022. Du lieu gom cac nhom bang:

- Master: `products.csv`, `customers.csv`, `promotions.csv`, `geography.csv`
- Transaction: `orders.csv`, `order_items.csv`, `payments.csv`, `shipments.csv`, `returns.csv`, `reviews.csv`
- Analytical: `sales.csv`, `sample_submission.csv`
- Operational: `inventory.csv`, `web_traffic.csv`

Phan du bao:

- Train: `sales.csv`, tu 04/07/2012 den 31/12/2022
- Test an tren Kaggle: tu 01/01/2023 den 01/07/2024

## 2. Phan 1 - Cau hoi trac nghiem

Chon 1 dap an dung nhat cho moi cau. Tat ca cau hoi deu yeu cau tinh toan truc tiep tu du lieu duoc cung cap.

1. Tinh trung vi so ngay giua hai lan mua lien tiep cua nhom khach hang co hon 1 don hang, dua tren `orders.csv`.
   Dap an lua chon: 30 ngay, 90 ngay, 144 ngay, 365 ngay.

2. Tim `segment` trong `products.csv` co ty suat loi nhuan gop trung binh cao nhat, theo cong thuc `(price - cogs) / price`.
   Dap an lua chon: Premium, Performance, Activewear, Standard.

3. Join `returns.csv` voi `products.csv` theo `product_id`, loc san pham thuoc danh muc Streetwear, roi tim ly do tra hang xuat hien nhieu nhat.
   Dap an lua chon: defective, wrong_size, changed_mind, not_as_described.

4. Trong `web_traffic.csv`, tim `traffic_source` co `bounce_rate` trung binh thap nhat.
   Dap an lua chon: organic_search, paid_search, email_campaign, social_media.

5. Tinh ty le phan tram dong trong `order_items.csv` co ap dung khuyen mai, tuc `promo_id` khong null.
   Dap an lua chon: 12%, 25%, 39%, 54%.

6. Trong `customers.csv`, voi cac khach hang co `age_group` khong null, tim nhom tuoi co so don hang trung binh tren moi khach hang cao nhat.
   Dap an lua chon: 55+, 25-34, 35-44, 45-54.

7. Tim vung `region` trong `geography.csv` tao ra tong doanh thu cao nhat trong tap sales train.
   Dap an lua chon: West, Central, East, ca ba vung co doanh thu xap xi bang nhau.

8. Trong cac don hang co `order_status = cancelled` trong `orders.csv`, tim phuong thuc thanh toan duoc dung nhieu nhat.
   Dap an lua chon: credit_card, cod, paypal, bank_transfer.

9. Trong cac size S, M, L, XL, tim size co ty le tra hang cao nhat. Ty le = so ban ghi trong `returns.csv` / so dong trong `order_items.csv`, sau khi join voi `products.csv` theo `product_id`.
   Dap an lua chon: S, M, L, XL.

10. Trong `payments.csv`, tim ke hoach tra gop co gia tri thanh toan trung binh moi don hang cao nhat.
    Dap an lua chon: 1 ky, 3 ky, 6 ky, 12 ky.

## 3. Phan 2 - Truc quan hoa va phan tich du lieu

Muc tieu: khai pha bo du lieu de tim insight co y nghia kinh doanh. Khong co mot dap an duy nhat; ban giam khao cham theo kha nang data storytelling, chieu sau phan tich va chat luong trinh bay.

Bai nop can co 2 thanh phan:

1. Truc quan hoa:
   - Tao bieu do, dashboard, ban do hoac cac hinh truc quan the hien pattern, xu huong, moi quan he trong du lieu.
   - Moi hinh can co tieu de, nhan truc ro rang, chu thich phu hop.

2. Phan tich:
   - Giai thich bieu do dang the hien dieu gi va vi sao goc nhin do quan trong.
   - Neu key findings bang so lieu cu the.
   - Neu business implications hoac actionable recommendations.

Bon cap do phan tich duoc danh gia:

- Descriptive: What happened? Thong ke tong hop dung, bieu do ro rang, tong hop du lieu chinh xac.
- Diagnostic: Why did it happen? Co gia thuyet, so sanh phan khuc, phat hien bat thuong co bang chung.
- Predictive: What is likely to happen? Co ngoai suy xu huong, mua vu, chi so dan xuat.
- Prescriptive: What should we do? Co de xuat hanh dong kinh doanh duoc du lieu ho tro, dinh luong duoc trade-off.

Diem cao nhat thuong den tu bai co cap do Prescriptive nhat quan tren nhieu phan tich.

## 4. Phan 3 - Mo hinh du bao doanh thu

Boi canh: dong vai nha khoa hoc du lieu tai cong ty thoi trang thuong mai dien tu Viet Nam. Doanh nghiep can du bao nhu cau/doanh thu chinh xac de toi uu ton kho, khuyen mai va logistics.

Yeu cau chinh:

- Du bao cot `Revenue` cho giai doan test an tu 01/01/2023 den 01/07/2024.
- File nop la `submission.csv`, giu dung thu tu dong nhu `sample_submission.csv`.
- Dinh dang file nop gom cac cot: `Date`, `Revenue`, `COGS`.

Chi so danh gia:

- MAE: cang thap cang tot.
- RMSE: cang thap cang tot, phat nang hon voi sai so lon.
- R2: cang cao cang tot, ly tuong gan 1.

Rang buoc:

- Khong dung du lieu ngoai.
- Toan bo feature phai tao tu cac file duoc cung cap.
- Ket qua phai tai lap duoc, can dinh kem code va dat random seed khi can.
- Report can co giai thich mo hinh bang feature importance, SHAP, partial dependence plot hoac cach tuong duong.
- Giai thich cac yeu to dan dong doanh thu bang ngon ngu kinh doanh.

Dieu kien loai Phan 3:

- Su dung `Revenue`/`COGS` cua tap test lam feature.
- Su dung du lieu ngoai bo du lieu duoc cung cap.
- Khong dinh kem ma nguon hoac ket qua khong the tai lap.

