## 7. Cach cham Phan 2 - EDA va Data Storytelling

Diem toi da: 60 diem, gom 4 tieu chi:

| Tieu chi | Diem toi da | Noi dung cham |
|---|---:|---|
| Chat luong truc quan hoa | 15 | Bieu do co tieu de, nhan truc, chu thich; chon dung loai bieu do; trinh bay ro rang |
| Chieu sau phan tich | 25 | Bao phu Descriptive, Diagnostic, Predictive, Prescriptive; lap luan logic; co so lieu ho tro |
| Insight kinh doanh | 15 | Phat hien co gia tri thuc tien; de xuat hanh dong kha thi; lien ket du lieu voi quyet dinh kinh doanh |
| Tinh sang tao va ke chuyen | 5 | Goc nhin doc dao, khong lap lai phan tich hien nhien; mach trinh bay coherent; ket hop nhieu bang co chu dich |

Chi tiet muc diem:

### Chat luong truc quan hoa - 15 diem

- 13-15 diem: tat ca bieu do dat chuan, chon loai bieu do toi uu cho tung insight.
- 8-12 diem: phan lon bieu do dat yeu cau, con thieu mot so nhan/chuthich.
- 0-7 diem: bieu do thieu thong tin, kho doc hoac khong phu hop voi du lieu.

### Chieu sau phan tich - 25 diem

- 21-25 diem: dat ca 4 cap do Descriptive, Diagnostic, Predictive, Prescriptive mot cach nhat quan.
- 14-20 diem: dat 3 cap do, phan Prescriptive con hoi hot.
- 7-13 diem: chu yeu o cap Descriptive va Diagnostic.
- 0-6 diem: chi mo ta be mat, thieu phan tich.

### Insight kinh doanh - 15 diem

- 13-15 diem: de xuat cu the, dinh luong duoc, co the ap dung ngay.
- 8-12 diem: co de xuat nhung con chung chung.
- 0-7 diem: thieu ket noi voi boi canh kinh doanh.

### Tinh sang tao va ke chuyen - 5 diem

- 4-5 diem: goc nhin doc dao, ket hop nhieu nguon du lieu, mach trinh bay thuyet phuc.
- 2-3 diem: co diem sang tao nhung chua nhat quan.
- 0-1 diem: phan tich de doan, khong co diem noi bat.

## 8. Cach cham Phan 3 - Forecasting

Diem toi da: 20 diem, gom 2 thanh phan:

| Thanh phan | Diem toi da | Noi dung cham |
|---|---:|---|
| Hieu suat mo hinh | 12 | Dua tren MAE, RMSE, R2 tren tap test va xep hang tuong doi tren Kaggle leaderboard |
| Bao cao ky thuat | 8 | Chat luong pipeline, feature engineering, cross-validation, xu ly leakage, explainability va tuan thu rang buoc |

Chi tiet muc diem:

### Hieu suat mo hinh - 12 diem

- 10-12 diem: top leaderboard, MAE/RMSE thap, R2 cao.
- 5-9 diem: hieu suat trung binh, mo hinh hoat dong nhung chua toi uu.
- 3-4 diem: bai nop hop le nhung hieu suat thap.

### Bao cao ky thuat - 8 diem

- 7-8 diem: pipeline ro rang, cross-validation dung chieu thoi gian, co giai thich mo hinh bang SHAP/feature importance hoac tuong duong, tuan thu rang buoc.
- 4-6 diem: pipeline du dung, giai thich con dinh tinh, mot so rang buoc chua xu ly ro.
- 0-3 diem: thieu giai thich, khong kiem soat leakage, hoac khong the tai lap ket qua.

